## Storybook
- Create stories for all components
- Document component props and usage
- Include various states and variants
- Test accessibility with `@storybook/addon-a11y`
- Use `@storybook/addon-docs` for documentation
- Implement component tests with `@storybook/addon-vitest`
- Use proper story organization and naming

## Testing
- Write unit tests for components
- Test user interactions
- Test accessibility
- Test error states
- Use proper test data
- Implement proper test isolation
- Use proper test descriptions

## Linting
- Follow ESLint configuration
- Fix linting errors automatically
- Use proper import ordering
- Follow naming conventions
- Use proper TypeScript types
- Implement proper error handling
- Use proper code formatting

## CI/CD
- Run tests in CI pipeline
- Check code coverage
- Run accessibility tests
- Validate TypeScript types
- Check bundle size
- Run performance tests
- Validate documentation
